It is expected that you participate in some way – be a lead, be a speaker/contributor, or at a minimum be an active participant.\\r\",\"marks\":[]}]},{\"object\":\"block\",\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"data\":{},\"nodes\":[{\"object\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\\r\",\"marks\":[]}]},{\"object\":\"block\",\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"data\":{},\"nodes\":[{\"object\":\"text\",\"text\":\"We believe that our time on the Liberty Mutual account is more than just delivering high-quality products, and that the whole of our account is greater than the sum of our individual teams.  To that end, we created the\",\"marks\":[]},{\"object\":\"text\",\"text\":\" Liberty Experience \",\"marks\":[{\"object\":\"mark\",\"type\":\"uui-richTextEditor-bold\",\"data\":{}}]},{\"object\":\"text\",\"text\":\"to support and enable a well-rounded and complete experience for our team members.\\r\",\"marks\":[]}]},{\"object\":\"block\",\"type\":\"image\",\"data\":{\"size\":128768,\"src\":\"https://onboarding.epam.com/app/cdn/cc1dc028-416a-438f-b618-2c7412482550/iiiii.PNG?preview=true\",\"path\":\"https://onboarding.epam.com/app/cdn/cc1dc028-416a-438f-b618-2c7412482550/iiiii.PNG?preview=true\",\"fileName\":\"iiiii.PNG\",\"name\":\"iiiii.PNG\",\"mimeType\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"subtype\":\"png\",\"parameters\":{},\"qualityValue\":1,\"wildcardType\":false,\"wildcardSubtype\":false,\"concrete\":true,\"charset\":null},\"type\":\"image\",\"id\":\"cc1dc028-416a-438f-b618-2c7412482550\",\"imageSize\":{\"width\":1029,\"height\":343.25712143928035},\"extension\":\"PNG\"},\"nodes\":[{\"object\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\",\"marks\":[]}]}]}}"
